author: ate
msg: JS2-550: A new Two-way password encoding service allowing decoding of encoded passwords
This set of changes provides a further enhancement providing a way to lazy upgrade from one encoding scheme to another.
Furthermore, a few improvements in handling of InternalCredential timestamp properties.
